00:00:01.480 --> 00:00:04.720
Welcome to all of you.

00:00:20.440 --> 00:00:25.400
This great country is also passing through a crisis.

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:29.680
Nowadays I feel there are so many things that are happening

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:33.000
which you could never dream before.

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:36.160
And at this time you all have arrived

00:00:36.360 --> 00:00:40.960
bringing peace and joy to all of them.

00:00:41.320 --> 00:00:45.800
So I thank you for that.

00:00:56.680 --> 00:01:02.680
The strife and the strain which is on human beings is

00:01:03.080 --> 00:01:11.040
perhaps because they are not yet worthy of God's blessings.

00:01:11.440 --> 00:01:15.560
Still, as God has created them,

00:01:16.280 --> 00:01:20.000
He tries to do His utmost

00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:23.360
to see that human beings are kept comfortably

00:01:23.560 --> 00:01:26.640
alright on this Mother Earth.

00:01:26.920 --> 00:01:30.520
He creates all kinds of beautiful things as you see

00:01:30.840 --> 00:01:34.560
and the whole cosmos is in unison

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:39.440
and working out something very great today.

00:01:39.880 --> 00:01:43.480
This new revolution that has started,

00:01:44.040 --> 00:01:47.160
very, very silently,

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:50.560
today is taking it's shape

00:01:50.760 --> 00:01:56.960
and is providing a new future for all of us.

00:01:57.240 --> 00:02:01.440
You see those big, big trees, that are on top of your head

00:02:01.800 --> 00:02:07.600
and as long as you are sitting here no fruit will fall upon you.

00:02:07.880 --> 00:02:10.160
It's not because I am here

00:02:10.360 --> 00:02:13.120
but because this Mother Earth knows

00:02:13.320 --> 00:02:15.960
that there are such great saints sitting here

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:19.880
and She is not going to disturb.

00:02:25.600 --> 00:02:29.000
This place was called as Shrigaav I was told,

00:02:29.320 --> 00:02:34.720
means the village of the Goddess.

00:02:35.080 --> 00:02:38.920
And this fruit is called as Shriphal,

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:41.880
meaning the fruit of the Goddess.

00:02:42.160 --> 00:02:48.520
But actually if you see, a coconut is something like our Sahasrara

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:56.680
and is very auspicious because it can absorb lot of vibrations,

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:01.120
as if it has got its realization.

00:03:01.320 --> 00:03:04.200
As you people can absorb My vibrations,

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:09.400
this fruit can absorb also My vibrations,

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:14.400
in the greatest amount.

00:03:14.680 --> 00:03:18.600
So we are here today

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:22.480
in a very big way

00:03:27.080 --> 00:03:33.320
to advertise the coming of the New Age.

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:39.360
The coming of

00:03:39.960 --> 00:03:45.359
the Golden Era, people have talked about.

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:49.240
Here we are to say

00:03:49.480 --> 00:03:55.280
what is reality, what is truth, what is joy.

00:03:55.880 --> 00:04:01.520
Here we are to manifest that and also

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:11.720
to create a commotion or a movement

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:19.320
in the cosmos so that this new awareness

00:04:20.280 --> 00:04:25.520
is established in the cosmos

00:04:25.880 --> 00:04:29.160
which will enlighten this country

00:04:29.360 --> 00:04:32.160
and the people of this country.

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:37.960
Also you will pick up the threads of this movement within yourself

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:43.120
which is a very subtle movement going on.

00:04:44.520 --> 00:04:49.560
At this moment we are in a strife of an intellectual

00:04:49.760 --> 00:04:53.560
who tried to describe

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:59.000
Shri Rama and Shri Krishna, in a slurring manner.

00:04:59.720 --> 00:05:06.320
And this is the time I want to bring your attention

00:05:06.760 --> 00:05:14.720
that if this intellectual strife to use the intelligence

00:05:14.960 --> 00:05:21.200
to bring down all the ideals which enlighten our path,

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:25.920
which gives us the guideline and an aspiration,

00:05:26.400 --> 00:05:33.440
then our lives become absolutely mundane, useless, joyless.

00:05:35.840 --> 00:05:40.489
It's very easy to condemn an ideal life,

00:05:41.320 --> 00:05:45.480
but to attain that life is very difficult.

00:05:46.480 --> 00:05:49.880
And some people, because they cannot attain it,

00:05:50.080 --> 00:05:56.760
try to condemn it so that they feel that they are no less,

00:05:57.040 --> 00:06:00.840
no way less than those great lives.

00:06:03.560 --> 00:06:08.360
All these ideals are created, these images are created,

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:14.400
everywhere in the world by the Divine power

00:06:16.040 --> 00:06:19.840
and people look at them

00:06:20.040 --> 00:06:27.320
and think that these great lives are beautiful,

00:06:27.640 --> 00:06:34.040
though they have suffered a lot, but there is so much of

00:06:34.600 --> 00:06:39.520
deeper understanding

00:06:39.880 --> 00:06:46.680
and deeper balancing and a deeper love.

00:06:49.400 --> 00:06:56.440
These ideals are very important for human societies

00:06:56.720 --> 00:07:00.360
otherwise they will be absolutely living in a relatively

00:07:00.600 --> 00:07:06.600
and they will have no absolute measure

00:07:07.080 --> 00:07:11.040
to find out what is right and what is wrong.

00:07:13.120 --> 00:07:16.320
In Sahaja Yoga we are here first of all

00:07:16.520 --> 00:07:18.960
to get connected with God Almighty,

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:23.280
with His power, the All-Pervading Power of Chaitanya.

00:07:23.720 --> 00:07:28.960
By that we become our own master,

00:07:29.280 --> 00:07:34.760
in the sense that we get our own guidelines.

00:07:35.040 --> 00:07:38.200
If some Sahaja Yogi has not achieved that much

00:07:38.440 --> 00:07:41.240
then is a serious thing.

00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:44.240
At least a Sahaja Yogi should be able to see,

00:07:44.440 --> 00:07:50.200
at the minimum of minimum, what is wrong with that person.

00:07:54.520 --> 00:08:00.960
To cleanse yourself and to put yourself right is of course,

00:08:01.560 --> 00:08:08.280
is a very important duty of every Sahaja Yogi.

00:08:08.680 --> 00:08:11.240
But these things are not to be taken

00:08:11.440 --> 00:08:14.759
as condemnation of yourself by any chance.

00:08:14.960 --> 00:08:18.760
And you should not be identified with those problems that you have

00:08:18.960 --> 00:08:25.276
but try to face them and cure them.

00:08:26.760 --> 00:08:28.880
Many a times I have heard Sahaja Yogis saying

00:08:29.080 --> 00:08:31.480
that Indians are very simple people

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:33.720
they are not complicated, Mother,

00:08:34.000 --> 00:08:39.760
so they can achieve their ascent much faster.

00:08:40.280 --> 00:08:48.040
But it's not that. It is very different for all of you, very much.

00:08:48.560 --> 00:08:51.760
And despite all the complications, and all kinds of brain washing,

00:08:51.960 --> 00:08:55.400
and all kinds of book reading and all kinds of so-called seeking,

00:08:55.600 --> 00:08:58.800
and all that nonsense one has gone through,

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:01.680
you have come out of it,

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:05.040
you have washed yourself completely

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:12.480
and today you are there united together to face

00:09:12.760 --> 00:09:15.440
all that is absurd,

00:09:15.640 --> 00:09:19.320
all that is false, all that is wrong.

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:25.880
It has to be a very formidable army for us

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:30.600
because if you see around, even in this country,

00:09:30.800 --> 00:09:32.840
you call it not complicated,

00:09:33.040 --> 00:09:36.760
there are many who are all the time to complicate others

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:43.640
and to destroy all their ideals, destroy all their visions

00:09:43.880 --> 00:09:49.160
and brainwash them.

00:09:49.760 --> 00:09:54.280
So you have to be very alert yourself

00:09:54.480 --> 00:09:57.640
and you have to be very conscious,

00:09:57.840 --> 00:10:04.840
that it is you who is going to build up this great image

00:10:05.080 --> 00:10:09.880
of ideal people,

00:10:10.160 --> 00:10:16.720
not one ideal life but ideal people in all collectivities.

00:10:17.400 --> 00:10:21.920
Now on your way to our tour,

00:10:22.120 --> 00:10:29.160
you are now on the threshold of entering into a new dimension,

00:10:29.800 --> 00:10:32.720
it is a subtler dimension,

00:10:33.200 --> 00:10:38.215
and this subtler dimension is within ourselves.

00:10:38.840 --> 00:10:45.400
And there lies your own being as your Spirit.

00:10:46.120 --> 00:10:49.520
It sees you as separate,

00:10:49.920 --> 00:10:54.000
your Self is separate from yourself.

00:10:54.280 --> 00:11:00.120
All these identifications have to be dropped out,

00:11:00.600 --> 00:11:03.920
all kinds of misidentifications.

