00:11:37.200 --> 00:11:41.720
then I must say that we have to give up those limitations.

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:48.200
The time has come. Of course you have the choice.

00:11:49.160 --> 00:11:52.560
Nobody is going to force you to do anything

00:11:52.760 --> 00:11:57.600
but it also expresses your personality

00:11:58.440 --> 00:12:05.440
that you still are lingering on to these small, small limitations.

00:12:07.440 --> 00:12:11.240
As I have told you many a times

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:14.680
God created only one world.

00:12:14.960 --> 00:12:19.760
Of course He created varieties just to create beauty.

00:12:20.280 --> 00:12:24.000
But how blind we are

00:12:24.400 --> 00:12:29.120
that we think we are different people,

00:12:29.400 --> 00:12:34.040
we are of different countries, of different races,

00:12:34.400 --> 00:12:40.320
of different castes, communities, cities -

00:12:40.600 --> 00:12:47.360
then little, little rows, then houses.

00:12:47.800 --> 00:12:55.040
I would say we become from human beings to rats and rats to worms

00:12:55.280 --> 00:13:00.480
and then I don't know what is the situation later .

00:13:01.400 --> 00:13:06.080
Let's open our heart, let's become great,

00:13:06.520 --> 00:13:09.520
we have to be like lions,

00:13:09.840 --> 00:13:15.680
not to be small and creepy people like worms.

00:13:16.000 --> 00:13:19.440
There are many worms everywhere in the world.

00:13:19.680 --> 00:13:24.480
We are specially chosen people to be something great.

00:13:24.920 --> 00:13:29.920
So open your heart. That's the main problem.

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:33.320
This ego covers the heart

00:13:33.560 --> 00:13:39.040
and makes you feel that, “Now I am an Indian, I am a Christian,

00:13:39.240 --> 00:13:43.200
I am this thing, I am that thing.”

00:13:43.720 --> 00:13:51.600
Now if I say to someone that you are not to go to temple,

00:13:52.880 --> 00:13:55.600
then I must be

00:13:55.880 --> 00:14:01.320
a very cruel person to say that not to go to a temple.

00:14:04.120 --> 00:14:10.200
But they go to a temple and come back with such a big

00:14:11.960 --> 00:14:15.480
entity on their heads.

00:14:16.360 --> 00:14:19.080
Then they go to churches.

00:14:19.360 --> 00:14:21.560
The other day I had a very bad experience of a lady

00:14:21.760 --> 00:14:26.440
who went to a church in France

00:14:26.640 --> 00:14:29.720
and she has become

00:14:29.960 --> 00:14:33.840
something like a minister, maybe something like a pope.

00:14:34.800 --> 00:14:39.200
I mean something very funny you know, nothing normal.

00:14:39.960 --> 00:14:43.760
I couldn't discover it, when I asked she said, “I went to a church.”

00:14:43.960 --> 00:14:48.600
“Why?”
“Because they arranged a marriage there." “Why?”

00:14:48.920 --> 00:14:51.200
“Oh, they wanted to have a big social event

00:14:51.400 --> 00:14:53.160
so they wanted to have a marriage.”

00:14:53.360 --> 00:14:56.600
