00:15:41.680 --> 00:15:46.520
The other day I was telling a lady about her food,

00:15:46.880 --> 00:15:51.440
that a new idea has come that you should not eat any salt and sugar,

00:15:51.720 --> 00:15:54.440
I mean just imagine!

00:15:54.680 --> 00:15:58.560
